      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Thank you so much for helping me with all my requests so far. Oh yeah, a promise is a promise... here's my dad's book. I have no idea what this book is about, but... why is he so gaga over this anyway??"
