      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Ohhh... this is the book! The book I was looking for... phew, thank you so much. I knew you'd bring it to me... Here, a piece of clothing like I promised... and this isn't much, but... here you go."
