          "_dirName": "item",
          "_dirType": "sub",
          "0": {
            "_dirName": "0",
            "_dirType": "String",
            "_value": "You haven't found out my son yet, huh. He took a very important book out with him. I'll definitely reward you handsomely for your work. He may be in a passage made of trees near the forest at #m10002000#."
